h3 State custom behavior
p.-text
  | The four expansion panel states behave similarly to each other, although there are two main differences
  | between them.
ol.-text
  li
    | The title will render in the brand color for the active panel, in soft gray for the disabled panel and black for
    | the other panel states.
  li Two internal hiding utility classes will hide content depending on the state.

